@baude, I see your question above:

> Any chance the operation system went to "sleep" with the vm running prior to the error?

I have a colleague who experienced this issue today and verifies that he accidentally put his MacBook to sleep when he went to lunch, instead of locking the screen. I don't believe he's otherwise seen this issue.

@ashley-cui Any updates on this issue? The issue occurs when the podman machine is running. 
(podman Version: 3.4.4, Device MBP 2020, MacOS Monterey)

